{"tid":2279197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡前駐聯合國大使：美國不該強迫他國在美中之間做選擇","createTime":"2020-11-09T15:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T15:28:30.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af3158222a8ee58a875965e75a10566c90874aca","tid":2279197,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統候選人拜登宣布勝選，外界關注未來美中關係走向；財經媒體「CNBC」報導，新加坡前駐聯合國大使馬凱碩（Kishore Mahbubani）表示，<span class=\"red\">華府不應該強迫其他國家在美中之間選邊站，這讓所有人都非常不自在。</span><br />\n<br />\n馬凱碩曾是新加坡前駐聯合國大使，現為新加坡國立大學公共政策教授、作家。馬凱碩週一接受「CNBC」訪問時表示，川普對中政策反覆不定，讓許多國家陷入困境，被迫在美國和中國之間做選擇，此舉令人非常不舒服。<br />\n<br />\n自川普2017年就職以來，美中關係明顯惡化，且在某些情況下，美國試圖拉攏盟友一起反對中國；例如美國先前不斷鼓吹盟友，在5G網路當中拒用中國華為產品，而且在選舉前沒多久，美國國務卿龐皮歐也旋風式訪問南亞和東南亞4國，欲鞏固盟友抗中。<br />\n<br />\n馬凱碩指出，由於美國投入很多資源，因此受到東南亞國家歡迎，但他認為美國不該利用這些對美國的善意。<span class=\"red\">他補充表示，美國必須做「長遠考量」，不應該強迫各國選擇立場，對美國而言，更好的做法是與夥伴國家連手制定全球（包括中國）都必須遵守的規範。</span><br />\n<br />\n長期參與跨太平洋夥伴關係協定（TPP）有助於美國鞏固在東南亞的地位，然而川普在任時美國已經退出TPP；馬凱碩指出，拜登如果想要重返TPP將「非常困難」，如果讓拜豋私下決定，拜豋會願意回到TPP，但將面臨在國內被圍剿的局面，他也認為，美國現在反對自由貿易的政治環境是極其有害的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3346680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3346680&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=a79db170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3346680&h=869ec9bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3346680</a><br />\n<br />\nCNBC:<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/09/washington-shouldnt-force-countries-to-choose-us-or-china-ex-diplomat.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F11%2F09%2Fwashington-shouldnt-force-countries-to-choose-us-or-china-ex-diplomat.html&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=82989e48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/09/washington-shouldnt-force-countries-to-choose-us-or-china-ex-diplomat.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">幫拜登既「圍堵」中國政策吹風?</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJ2pyyq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJ2pyyq.png&h=e807a9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">另外，奧巴馬既TPP真是可以有效圍堵到中國?中國馬上就搞個RCEP應對</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee7a8f2669515b133ee9588096693b6dbf2877d","tid":2279197,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"想兩邊奶?"},{"pid":"d1b17fb608e97c252bdb49973cdf4fdd983ecfb7","tid":2279197,"uid":323720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7ee7a8f2669515b133ee9588096693b6dbf2877d","tid":2279197,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"想兩邊奶?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"擺明，賺錢靠中國，國防靠美國"},{"pid":"b366fa8144a47dd472e19aed73e93c815f7f4820","tid":2279197,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"又想食兩家茶禮"},{"pid":"695797a5aa0cdc19be35c87049e64727e115f3ee","tid":2279197,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"monkeypore又想食兩家茶禮？"},{"pid":"d1011c9fe9d566acd22be5504350513109280276","tid":2279197,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"牆頭草又發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21faa5a9bd3de08776c8960c6a656672621bd991","tid":2279197,"uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"又唔見你同習近平講？"}]}